snippet.textDisplay: Tati Beauty is a stunning palette- I havent touched any other palette for 2 months since receiving it for my birthday. I use the sequin formula every single day instead of the matte and throughout the day I'll notice my eyes have that dewy romantic expensive look to them - because the sequins don't leave when you blend the shadow, they simply spread out and multiply. That formula is more fun for other people looking at you than for you looking into the mirror. But it's a classy way for an office girl like me to get her sparkle without alarming anyone who walks in. And for date nights I get to use the glitter and it wears for 12+ hours no problem. I've even gone to the gym wearing this palette and there was zero creasing
